    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>half </strong>your<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in a small bowl with your<strong> mayo</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>remaining rice vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spring onion & ginger mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1688128501442-x200.jpg",
