      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>gochujang paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>remaining ginger & garlic paste</strong> in a bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Mix until fully combined – this is your <strong>gochujang glaze</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
