    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are browned, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>gochujang glaze</strong> to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 5-6 min further or until the pulled mushrooms are crisp and glazed – these are your <strong>Korean-style mushrooms</strong></p>",
