    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sandwich the <strong>Korean-style pulled mushrooms</strong>, some <strong>spring onion & ginger mayo</strong> and a little <strong>quick-pickled salad</strong> between the<strong> toasted brioche halves </strong>- this is your<strong> Korean-style pulled mushroom sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sesame potatoes</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>quick-pickled salad</strong> and <strong>remaining spring onion & ginger mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
